title: As of now I'm commandeering the Roleplay Boards.
body:
I would like to thank Aqualious18 for providing me with this wonderful suggestion. 

Onward, hello tenants of the Roleplay boards, I need to brainwash you so you may join me in taking over M&G to fashion in my image. 

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QrW727WFVJ0

Fall in the comment section to let me know you synapses have been rendered to me.
